 /> 喚起左大家嘅注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"我個人意見係 如果send email去保安局<br />\n就一定要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">提出問題</span></strong>俾保安局，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要求回覆</span></strong><br />\n唔好只提出意見<br />\n咁先可以提升佢地嘅行政成本<br />\n政府部門接收到查詢後，係一定要俾回覆的<br />\n而且仲係好小心咁諗過度過先覆 呢啲咁具爭議性嘅政策問題仲要好多時要經超過一層review先可以deploy個reply e.g 搵個EO I/II寫完draft仲要俾S/C rank嘅approve先出得街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要中文電郵中文覆 英文電郵英文覆<br />\n所以一定要問問題<br />\n最好同一封email 出一封中文 一封英文"},{"pid":"780574903cb82cc622bac313d62c69a4dd8d2c33","tid":1025269,"uid":38103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:01:11.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"42d2ef0d7590d7b89261fa28ed1db9ae645494c2","tid":1025269,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:01:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60f21c18c68bd5c780a556eee176f2e19f2968cc","tid":1025269,"uid":45635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:03:06.000Z","msg":"睇左一次性交逃犯安排<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae13b9460ecb840ad4636ae6ef6e20a7b791b22","tid":1025269,"uid":153583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27c78ac486a6e6295e8939b6cddc712bb9a7d58c","tid":1025269,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1d6e237b3a0d7b3331f0709bd7f37616dd2662b","tid":1025269,"uid":153583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3fb38406443127cf1d3138a7f029599a438c04a5","tid":1025269,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己香港自己推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T10:51:17.000Z","msg":"巴打之前個post寫得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喚起左大家嘅注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"我個人意見係 如果send email去保安局<br />\n就一定要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">提出問題</span></strong>俾保安局，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要求回覆</span></strong><br />\n唔好只提出意見<br />\n咁先可以提升佢地嘅行政成本<br />\n政府部門接收到查詢後，係一定要俾回覆的<br />\n而且仲係好小心咁諗過度過先覆 呢啲咁具爭議性嘅政策問題仲要好多時要經超過一層review先可以deploy個reply e.g 搵個EO I/II寫完draft仲要俾S/C rank嘅approve先出得街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要中文電郵中文覆 英文電郵英文覆<br />\n所以一定要問問題<br />\n最好同一封email 出一封中文 一封英文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:07:56.000Z","msg":"但係要求回覆嘅話係咪應該要send去另外一個email? 即係官方處理查詢嗰個email?<br />\n<br />\n我而家搵到呢個email係講明用嚟收集今次嘅意見，唔知佢會唔會覆人"}]}